  "text": "In this section, we go back to the in expectation convergence analysis which is standard for the stochastic settings. For smooth functions with strong convexity, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] provided guarantees for linear rate of convergence. We restate the theorem here and show that the theorem still holds for the non-convex landscape obtained by MKL-SGD in noiseless setting.",
